body_html:
I have the same issue. And it is independent from a concrete device:

  • OS Platform and Distribution: OSX High Sierra 10.13.6
  • Mobile device: iPhone 7, iOS 12.x
  • TensorFlow installed from (source or binary):
    https://www.tensorflow.org/lite/demo_ios
  • TensorFlow version: 1.12.0
    Other options have no influence because the project is not even compiled due to incorrect paths to files.
